# Stale path-bug masking entries removed: /metrics, /metrics/run-history,
# /metrics/vram-history.jsonl. metrics/ at root is a verifier violation
# (only output/metrics/ is canonical). Keeping these in .gitignore was
# silencing check-root-only-dirs.js, letting writers accumulate files at
# the wrong path.

# KB lance tables — ephemeral generated state, never hand-authored.
# The .lance directories are regenerated by rag_engines indexing and compacted
# by scripts/compact-lance-tables.py. Tracking their internals (_deletions/,
# _transactions/, _versions/, data/) produces gigabytes of binary drift per
# indexer run and causes patch-based commit tools (GitLens) to fail with
# "cannot apply binary patch ... without full index line" when pre-image
# SHAs drift. Gitignored en masse.
/tools/HME/KB/*.lance/
